Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:04.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙世纪0079年12月24日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:09.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要与这艘船共存亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:15.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在完成任务之前你们绝不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:21.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:25.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要磨磨蹭蹭的 已经给你们做好了逃离准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:35.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要避免姆赛小艇被击中！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:38.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子姆赛 出发准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:44.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劣势只是一时的 胜利必将属于我们吉翁！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.79,0:00:48.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些小鬼应当能亲眼见证
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:49.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:28.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 别摔着咯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.01,0:01:29.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:33.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说是一份价钱两份货了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:36.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以干脆给我三份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:50.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是宇宙世纪00... 00多少年来着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:53.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之战争已结束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:56.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的兵器成了一堆废铁...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:07.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有士兵的战场所剩的只有空虚...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:11.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的小队被解散了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:17.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队友们都因战后处理而四散各方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:20.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自退伍的我背负着大家的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:25.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们下落不明的小队长...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:26.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:56.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 到现在还在迷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BB...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:03.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BB可不会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:14.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的东西... 讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:22.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:30.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是宇宙船的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:34.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙船？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:42.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉翁的宇宙艇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:53.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:54.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:03:59.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉翁兵...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:16.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉格博士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:20.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂... 快点离开这鬼地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:23.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得毛骨悚然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 有人...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:35.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚印
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:40.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:41.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵籍牌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:45.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这么多！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:49.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果 果然有人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:51.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊 琪琪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:54.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鹅？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:56.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:00.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚在这过夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:02.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:27.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:31.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:36.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:44.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:47.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:50.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉翁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:51.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:54.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带你们去见队长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:55.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:57.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:06.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这村子... 被战争所毁的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:10.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河流被改向了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:25.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟上来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:28.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是MS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:56.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所属和军阶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报出所属和军阶！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:01.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个老百姓而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是军人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:07.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫琪琪·洛基塔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:08.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙叫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:11.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:13.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:20.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是地球联邦极东方面军机械化混成大队第08MS小队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:22.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米凯尔·尼诺利齐伍长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:24.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是前伍长...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:27.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪琪和米凯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:29.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别撒谎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:30.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:32.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是是搜索吉翁的残党
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:33.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会只派两个人来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要搞错！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:43.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们什么时候来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:45.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等吉翁的救援吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:47.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:49.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吉翁已经战败了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:50.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:54.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的话就快点向联邦投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:57.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那样会安全...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:59.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:01.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会爆发战争的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:03.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样我们又会被利用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:06.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里生活反而更平和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:11.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被强迫征兵可真是倒霉到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 比起那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:16.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前的现实更值得担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:19.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖着小孩和伤者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.21,0:08:20.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物看起来似乎也不够...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:26.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我出去过夜！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪琪 你太多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:38.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 给我松绑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:43.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就给点酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你们又不喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:55.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老实实待着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:59.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 这不是给我去拿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟琪琪不同 他很懂事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:06.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你这么啰嗦说不定他在酒里下毒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:09.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了 那些家伙做了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:14.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比方说像艾历多亚先生那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:17.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意挨几颗子弹好送去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:21.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或像队长那样敌前逃跑享受安逸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:23.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:28.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以既不能去联邦也不能去吉翁 一定是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:31.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 那宇宙艇 是他们击落的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:36.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是为了逃脱战争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:40.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员们大概是被那些家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:43.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长也在这里被捕...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:44.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:47.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西罗一定还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:51.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:57.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪琪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:06.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 手伸过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:07.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来弄断绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:10.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那种方法!? 开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:15.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:29.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 都出水泡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:31.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘！找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:33.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:44.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:45.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:57.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会 会被发现的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:11.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪琪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:17.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:22.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 那孩子就太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:33.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你们住手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:55.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是 葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:12:00.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不是只要埋掉就可以了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:05.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你们和这孩子是什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:08.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:09.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:10.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:16.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们的表情该悲伤一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:17.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:21.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么无动于衷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:25.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然悲伤！但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:29.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的心意合一... 意识合一...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:30.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时常...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:36.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远活在我们心中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:39.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:40.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:42.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:44.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 这 这个人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:51.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们见过这照片里的男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:55.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫西罗·阿玛达
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:57.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么 什么都好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:59.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的话就告诉我 求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:07.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你同伴的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:09.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是重要的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:13.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道的吧 队长如今在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:16.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:19.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:21.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是他的坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:22.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒谎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢这么说！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:27.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我们的队长做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:30.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的队长... 已经死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:31.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:32.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米凯尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:33.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:51.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你干什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:53.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想 想对我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:58.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:01.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:08.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:18.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:22.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个放在叶子上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:24.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后说“请吃吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:27.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:29.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:32.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:38.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:42.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来玩家家酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于那位死去的爱娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:11.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:14.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜可不是那种小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子不是爱娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:19.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我她的真名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爱娜！那孩子是爱娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:25.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦白告诉我实情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你隐瞒了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:28.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:31.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要找的男人在坟墓里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:34.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那请告诉我 西罗是怎么死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:36.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:38.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你杀了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:39.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:39.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:41.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:44.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要找的男人真的已经死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:46.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以快点离开！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:08.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么呢 有那个必要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:12.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呀 我不想再被“砰”地打晕掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:21.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:22.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:26.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不确认一下坟墓总是放心不下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:27.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是没错...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:31.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是队长若真埋在里面的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里面没有人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:43.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:38.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们生活在弗拉格博士的设施里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:40.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的事都记不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:42.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家族以及名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:43.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连名字也？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:46.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时都叫我们小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:50.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人们死时我们都不知该何去何从
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:53.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 遇上了西罗和爱娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:56.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们俩教会了我们很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:59.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何生火 如何捕鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何烧水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何包扎绷带
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:09.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他们俩建坟掩埋了自己的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是要改变自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:17.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变自己吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:18.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:21.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后赠予了我们名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:23.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:24.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫山达斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.82,0:18:27.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫艾历多亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:27.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:28.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米凯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:30.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子叫琪琪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:34.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜也把名字赠与那孩子来帮她打气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:38.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是队长的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:40.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪琪 把名字还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪琪是你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:45.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:46.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:48.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还给米凯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:52.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！不行！不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:54.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允许那样做！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:57.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的名字！不能还！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:19:00.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西罗·阿玛达是我的名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想我会还给你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:04.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:05.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:06.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:23.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西罗是我的名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:25.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:28.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我得到的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:32.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:35.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是西罗！我有名字的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:38.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字... 叫做西罗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我得到的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:44.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以别想我会还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:47.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西罗的名字只属于我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取回名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:53.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:56.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也做不到的 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:04.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你独自努力在守护着大家的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:06.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护着大家宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:09.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会给任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:11.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过已没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:13.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不会再有人那样做了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:21.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个很棒的队长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:23.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是西罗·阿玛达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:04.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:05.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:07.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米凯尔 看啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:08.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:11.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么冷你怎么一点都不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:57.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是队长教他们的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:02.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是那家伙的作风呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:10.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着 他们俩去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.37,0:22:13.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:14.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.94,0:22:16.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方有什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.93,0:22:21.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有新的世界 新的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.27,0:22:27.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像是队长的台词呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:06.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里都找不着他们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:09.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.66,0:23:11.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们睡着时...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.63,0:23:13.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他们是怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:20.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我... 在想...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.30,0:23:27.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是否是幻觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:30.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻觉?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.00,0:23:32.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.56,0:23:35.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就是幽灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:37.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.94,0:23:40.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一定也去寻找了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.86,0:23:42.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找？什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:44.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.45,0:23:47.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然是新的世界 新的人生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.18,0:23:50.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.56,0:24:47.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长~
